<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 09:14:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>欧洲汽车股因中国关税担忧而受挫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-autos-stocks-hit-china-tariff-jitters-2024-05-22/</link><description>欧洲汽车股是周三表现最差的股市板块，此前有报道称中国有可能对汽车征收更高的关税。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 09:06:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-autos-stocks-hit-china-tariff-jitters-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾海军中将指责中国大使馆在南海秘密通话录音</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-vice-admiral-accuses-chinese-embassy-secretly-recording-phone-call-2024-05-22/</link><description>菲律宾一名高级海军官员周三指责中国驻马尼拉大使馆未经他同意就对电话进行录音，并否认与北京达成了缓和南海紧张局势的协议。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 09:00:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-vice-admiral-accuses-chinese-embassy-secretly-recording-phone-call-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>研究机构称中国应将大型汽车关税提高至25%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-should-hike-tariffs-large-cars-25-says-research-body-2024-05-22/</link><description>一位政府下属的汽车研究机构专家对中国《环球时报》表示，中国应该将大型汽油动力汽车的进口关税提高到25%，因为中国面临着美国大幅提高的汽车进口关税，以及进入欧盟可能增加的关税。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 08:32:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-should-hike-tariffs-large-cars-25-says-research-body-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>Stellantis首席执行官：电动汽车关税是一个陷阱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-ceo-very-tough-battle-ahead-against-chinese-rivals-2024-05-22/</link><description>Stellantis 首席执行官卡洛斯·塔瓦雷斯 (Carlos Tavares) 周三表示，该集团预计将在欧洲电动汽车市场与中国竞争对手展开激烈竞争，并预计由此产生重大后果。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 07:53:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-ceo-very-tough-battle-ahead-against-chinese-rivals-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>LVMH 深化与阿里巴巴合作，提升科技在中国的影响力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/lvmh-deepens-partnership-with-alibaba-boost-tech-presence-china-2024-05-22/</link><description>法国奢侈品集团 LVMH 周三表示，将深化与阿里巴巴的合作伙伴关系，以利用该公司的云和人工智能能力，并扩大其在中国的业务。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 06:49:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/lvmh-deepens-partnership-with-alibaba-boost-tech-presence-china-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>小鹏汽车股价因技术服务收入和自动驾驶技术的乐观评论而飙升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-shares-surge-tech-service-income-upbeat-comments-self-driving-tech-2024-05-22/</link><description>周三，中国电动汽车制造商小鹏汽车的股价上涨逾 10%，原因是向大众汽车提供的研发服务带来的收入增长，以及对其自动驾驶技术目标的乐观评论。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 06:28:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-shares-surge-tech-service-income-upbeat-comments-self-driving-tech-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>七国集团财长寻求在俄罗斯资产和中国问题上达成共识</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-finance-chiefs-seek-common-line-russian-assets-china-2024-05-22/</link><description>官员们表示，七国集团财长本周在意大利举行会议，将试图就如何利用冻结的俄罗斯资产帮助乌克兰的战争努力以及如何应对中国在主要市场日益增长的出口实力问题找到共同点。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 05:35:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-finance-chiefs-seek-common-line-russian-assets-china-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>台湾关注梵蒂冈与中国的关系，称中国违反了主教协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-watches-vatican-china-ties-says-china-violated-deal-bishops-2024-05-22/</link><description>台湾外交部周三表示，台湾正在密切关注梵蒂冈与中国之间的互动，并补充说中国“一再违反”2018年关于主教任命的协议。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 04:09:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-watches-vatican-china-ties-says-china-violated-deal-bishops-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>对冲资金流 对冲基金连续第四周买入中国股票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hedge-flow-hedge-funds-buy-chinese-stocks-fourth-consecutive-week-2024-05-22/</link><description>全球对冲基金连续第四周增持中国股票，加入众多试图抢在市场反弹之前的投资者行列。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 03:55:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hedge-flow-hedge-funds-buy-chinese-stocks-fourth-consecutive-week-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>日本不满中国大使涉台言论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-complains-about-chinese-ambassadors-comment-relating-taiwan-2024-05-22/</link><description>日本内阁官房长官林吉正周三表示，日本已对中国大使有关台湾的“极不恰当”言论提出抗议。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 03:31:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-complains-about-chinese-ambassadors-comment-relating-taiwan-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>NHK报道，中日将讨论重启时隔六年的执政党会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-japan-discuss-resuming-ruling-party-talks-after-6-year-hiatus-nhk-reports-2024-05-22/</link><description>日本广播公司 NHK 周三报道称，一名中国共产党高级官员计划本月访问东京，会见日本执政党领导人，并讨论自 2018 年以来首次恢复两党之间的定期会谈。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 02:55:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-japan-discuss-resuming-ruling-party-talks-after-6-year-hiatus-nhk-reports-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>通胀担忧导致股市下滑，抵消了英伟达的希望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-22/</link><description>周三股市下跌，因英国强于预期的通胀抵消了投资者对人工智能重量级公司英伟达能够满足极高预期的希望，市场也在等待美联储何时开始降息的可能线索。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 02:46:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>游说团体警告英国公司预计在中国市场将遭遇困难</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/british-firms-expecting-hard-time-china-market-lobby-group-warns-2024-05-22/</link><description>英国一家商业游说团体周三表示，英国公司预计未来五年在中国开展业务将变得更加困难，因为北京方面正在努力阻止外国资金从曾经被视为全球增长引擎的市场撤出。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 01:06:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/british-firms-expecting-hard-time-china-market-lobby-group-warns-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>多头闯入中国股市，但外国人不敢进去</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/bulls-beat-path-china-stock-shop-foreigners-dare-not-go-2024-05-21/</link><description>受到中国最新措施和解决其陷入困境的经济最薄弱环节的承诺的鼓舞，国内投资者正在廉价股市中买入股票，而大多数外国投资者对此充满希望，但进展缓慢。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 23:11:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/bulls-beat-path-china-stock-shop-foreigners-dare-not-go-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>土耳其和中国在部长访问期间讨论采矿、核能和可再生能源</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/turkey-china-discuss-mining-nuclear-renewable-energy-during-ministers-visit-2024-05-21/</link><description>土耳其能源部长周二表示，本周与中国当局和企业就采矿项目、核能和可再生能源举行了会谈，两国签署了一项能源转换初步协议。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 14:37:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/turkey-china-discuss-mining-nuclear-renewable-energy-during-ministers-visit-2024-05-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>